<br>
I would suggest trying Neriak for spells. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujumorscarcarver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jumorscarcarver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 2:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bertoxx gnome wizzies... can't buy a thing!!</span><hr size=1> I haven't actually tried going IN to neriak, but the guards in Nektulous were threatening to me, which is worse than any other place I've been.  I'm assuming that means I can't even get close to Neriak. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ujumorscarcarver.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jumorscarcarver</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/22/02 2:57 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Bertoxx gnome wizzies... can't buy a thing!!</span><hr size=1> oh yeah....and about being level 20 without spells:  my friend has gone and bought them all for me and gave them to me.  But it's a major pain in the arse.<br>
